alfredsnippet.snippet:
SELECT dr2.*
from t66_ath_biz_info as biz
left join t66_ath_data_relation as dr on biz.BIZ_INFO_CODE = dr.DATA_CODE and dr.DATA_TYPE = 'BIZ_INFO' and dr.SZ_STATUS  = 1
left join t66_ath_data_relation as dr2 on dr.PROCEDURE_INSTANCE_CODE = dr2.PROCEDURE_INSTANCE_CODE and dr2.SZ_STATUS = 1
where biz.BIZ_CODE_TYPE = 'ORDER' and biz.SZ_STATUS = 1 and biz.BIZ_CODE = '395546495373'
alfredsnippet.name: 按订单号查识别号
